script.name: plugin.advjump.jump
script.sourceplaintext:
* lets check what kind of jump we are making if not [THIS] -> get amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive in cargo bay skip if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay return null if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive Energy Generator in cargo bay $advjump = [TRUE] else $advjump = [FALSE] end else $advjump = [TRUE] end
skip if $a.target return null
* jumping to position $targetPos = null $targetObj = null $jumpToPos = [FALSE] $targetSector = null $is.gateless = [FALSE] $is.current.gateless = [FALSE] if is datatype[ $a.target ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $targetPos = $a.target $targetSector = $a.target[3] $jumpToPos = [TRUE] else if $a.target -> is of class Ship do if $a.target -> is of type Jump Beacon $jumpBeacon = [TRUE] $targetPos = $a.target -> get position as array $targetSector = $a.target -> get sector $targetObj = $a.target $jumpToPos = [TRUE] else if $a.target -> is of class Station $targetPos = $a.target -> get position as array $targetSector = $a.target -> get sector $targetObj = $a.target $jumpToPos = [TRUE] else if $a.target -> is of class Gate $targetPos = $a.target -> get position as array $targetSector = $a.target -> get sector $targetObj = $a.target else if $a.target -> is of class Sector $targetSector = $a.target $targetPos = create new array, arguments=0, 0, 0, $targetSector, null else return null end
@ $tSectors = [THIS] -> call script plugin.advjump.getsectors : if $tSectors do if $tSectors[$targetSector] $is.gateless = [TRUE] do if $tSectors[[SECTOR]] $is.current.gateless = [TRUE] end
$size = size of array $targetPos if $size >= 4 $targetPos[3] = $targetSector else append $targetSector to array $targetPos end
@ $bestGate = [THIS] -> call script lib.cycrow.findbestgate : targetpos=$targetPos Jumpable Gate=[TRUE] if $a.target -> is of class Gate if [THIS] -> is gate/beacon: $a.target jumpable $bestGate = $a.target end end
* use normal jumpdrive if ! $advjump $energy = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $targetSector $gotEnergy = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay if $energy > $gotEnergy skip if [THIS] != [PLAYERSHIP] START speak text: page=13 id=1100056 priority=50 return null end
$skipJump = [FALSE] if [SECTOR] == $targetSector if $targetObj -> exists $dist = get distance between [THIS] and $targetObj $gate.dist = get distance between $bestGate and $targetObj if $dist <= $gate.dist $skipJump = [TRUE] end end end
if not $skipJump if $bestGate -> exists @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.jump : gate or sector=$bestGate followers should jump too=[TRUE] else if $jumpBeacon @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.jump : gate or sector=$targetSector followers should jump too=[TRUE] else @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.jumptogate.nearest : targetpos=$targetPos should followers jump too=[TRUE] end if $a.target -> is of class Gate return null else if $a.target -> is of class Sector return null end end
* use Advanced Jumpdrive else $route = null if $is.gateless $route = $targetSector else if $is.current.gateless $route = $targetSector else if $targetObj -> exists @ $route = [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$targetObj Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[TRUE] Allow Table=null Jump Flags=[JumpFlg.NoDeviceCheck] else if $targetPos @ $route = [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$targetPos Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[TRUE] Allow Table=null Jump Flags=[JumpFlg.NoDeviceCheck] else @ $route = [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$targetSector Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[TRUE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[TRUE] Allow Table=null Jump Flags=[JumpFlg.NoDeviceCheck] end
if not $route goto label no.route else if $route == [TRUE] $bestGate = null else if is datatype[ $route ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY if size of array $route $check.gate = $route[0] if $check.gate -> is of class Gate $bestGate = $check.gate $best.sector = $bestGate -> get sector do if $best.sector == [SECTOR] $bestGate = null end end end end
if $bestGate if [THIS] == [PLAYERSHIP] if [THIS] -> is docked @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.undock : end if [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive Accelertor in cargo bay START speak text: page=13 id=1261 priority=0 @ = wait 1000 ms play sample 965 @ = wait 1500 ms else START speak text: page=13 id=1319 priority=0 $time = 16000 while $time > 0 @ $time = wait $time ms end end else if [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive Accelertor in cargo bay @ = wait 3000 ms else @ = wait 17000 ms end end
if not [THIS] -> get amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive in cargo bay [THIS] ->set current shield strength to 0 [THIS] ->set laser energy to 0 end
* jump to the closest possible point if [SECTOR] != $targetSector $flags = [JumpFlg.NoDeviceCheck] | [JumpFlg.NoEnergyCheck] | [JumpFlg.NoJumpableCheck] | [JumpFlg.Quick] | [JumpFlg.NoEnergyUse] $energy.got = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay if $jumpBeacon = [THIS] ->jump: object=$targetObj flags=$flags else if $bestGate = [THIS] ->jump: object=$bestGate flags=$flags else = [THIS] ->jump: object=$targetSector flags=$flags end
if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Advanced Jumpdrive in cargo bay $energy.got2 = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $energy.needed = $energy.got - $energy.got2 do if $energy.needed > 0 = [THIS] -> add $energy.needed units of Energy Cells else if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive Energy Generator in cargo bay $energy.got2 = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $energy.needed = $energy.got - $energy.got2 do if $energy.needed > 0 = [THIS] -> add $energy.needed units of Energy Cells end
@ = wait 200 ms end
* if we didn't make it to the sector, then fly the rest of the way * skip if the script is already on the stack if not [THIS] -> is script !move.movetosector.simple on stack of task=0 if [SECTOR] != $targetSector @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector.simple : sector=$targetSector @ = wait 200 ms end end
$jump.target = $targetObj do if $bestGate -> exists $jump.target = $bestGate
*if $jump.target *if $jump.target -> is of class Gate *$x = $jump.target -> get x position *$y = $jump.target -> get y position *$z = $jump.target -> get z position *[THIS] ->set position: x=$x y=$y z=$z *$rotAlpha = $jump.target -> get rot alpha *$rotBeta = $jump.target -> get rot beta *$rotGamma = $jump.target -> get rot gamma *$rotAlpha = $rotAlpha + 32767 *if $rotAlpha > 65535 *$rotAlpha = $rotAlpha - 65535 *end *[THIS] ->set rotation: alpha=$rotAlpha beta=$rotBeta gamma=$rotGamma *end *end end end
set global variable: name='advjump.lastsector' value=$targetSector do if is datatype[ $a.target ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY set global variable: name='advjump.lastpos' value=$a.target do if $targetObj set global variable: name='advjump.lastobj' value=$targetObj
if $a.target -> exists do if $a.target -> is of class Sector return null end
* now move to the object if $jumpBeacon $x = $targetPos[0] $y = $targetPos[1] $z = $targetPos[2] *[THIS] ->set position: x=$x y=$y z=$z
else if not $a.target -> is of class Gate * targetting scanners if $advjump if [THIS] -> get amount of ware FTL Jumpdrive Extension in cargo bay @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.advjump.ftl : Sector Pos=$targetPos end end
* otherwise, just fly if $targetObj -> exists if $targetObj -> is of class Station @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$targetObj else @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoobject : Target=$targetObj Range=2000 end else if $targetPos $x = $targetPos[0] $y = $targetPos[1] $z = $targetPos[2] @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoposition : sector=$targetSector position x=$x position y=$y position z=$z precision=1000 end end
return [TRUE]
no.route: @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.cmd.moverejected : Destination=$targetSector return [FALSE]
